N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 21 ยง 1155.8 - Denial of use

State Regulations

The manager shall have authority to deny use of an air or
marine terminal to the owner or operator of any aircraft or watercraft
violating authority, State or Federal regulations whether at such terminal or
elsewhere. Notes
